{"tid":1676362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【散水論：支持XXXX，心入面知就得，唔使講出口】","createTime":"2019-10-26T11:37:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T13:53:13.000Z","uid":131691,"like":60,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"79a6b84756552deed7e53807bde742eaa94fb79f","tid":1676362,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T11:37:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FhR7cm3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFhR7cm3.jpg&h=f59a16be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<em>「時代革命」，心入面知就得，唔使講出口。<br />\n「香港國歌」，心入面知就得，唔使講出口。<br />\n支持加泰人民，心入面知就得，唔使講出口。<br />\n成立臨時政府，心入面知就得，唔使講出口。<br />\n支持香港獨立，心入面知就得，唔使講出口。</em><br />\n<br />\n<strong>風向撚箝制思想嘅技倆，其中一個方法就係喺預先限制手足討論嘅範圍</strong>，佢哋限制嘅原因滿佈邏輯謬誤（好似「唔使講出口」、「靜靜哋做」、「一定做唔到，所以唔使討論」），有意義嘅討論都隨即而中止。<br />\n<br />\n先唔講個政治，單單風向撚講嘅方法已經好荒謬，<strong>思想傳播唔靠語言、文字、象徵，唔經過討論，唔通靠心靈感應？</strong>又例如「光復香港，時代革命」唔係口號咁嗌出嚟，點去喚醒群眾同傳播革命意識？<br />\n<br />\n其次，<strong>思想係汰弱留強，多人認同就會跑出</strong>，但因為禁止群眾接觸而無從討論就係第二件事，𠵱個係蓄意操縱群眾嘅結果，群眾連分辨嘅機會都無。同國歌一樣，首歌意識形態符合大眾、旋律動人自然就多人唱，就好似《願榮光歸香港》；<strong>群眾都有自己政治同美學嘅判斷，唔係你搵啲網絡打手重覆一千次就會成為事實。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>風向撚越係禁制我哋嘅討論同傳播，我哋更加要大講特講</strong>，加泰集會嘅成功就證明𠵱班打手嘅操作唔會得逞。咁多位手足，只要我哋認為啱嘅事，我哋就要堅持去做，不論係網上討論、派傳單、貼連儂牆、甚至係組黨結社，將脫離中國管治、獨立建國嘅思想散播開去！<br />\n<br />\n====<br />\n轉載自《香港革命指南》<br />\n@hkmanual"},{"pid":"f0fc081ad1afe1d77f263bab2a2cb85efb801df0","tid":1676362,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T11:38:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3de618caa91b60c9edfc8c76ad2478c419e8fcc9","tid":1676362,"uid":167548,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T11:38:45.000Z","msg":"屌 有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申獨派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eba4093dfc342a92d047b07b9e8fd3d6c14de312","tid":1676362,"uid":84657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T11:39:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f10dee2fe60b12858a6c09340ddca889262f1d0","tid":1676362,"uid":213969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T11:39:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212b4e19e15999b9d2e6c9eb993f414997333e99","tid":1676362,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T11:40:50.000Z","msg":"加泰我都係驚影響歐洲觀感姐，sorry我有份叫大家唔好理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下次既主題就係東突同圖博了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e77a33ff755125637a56da4c85073f8540392c4","tid":1676362,"uid":35301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3de618caa91b60c9edfc8c76ad2478c419e8fcc9","tid":1676362,"uid":167548,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T11:38:45.000Z","msg":"屌 有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申獨派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T11:41:30.000Z","msg":"獨派<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc0dd322f6c856966b918029df4afc340bad081","tid":1676362,"uid":86509,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T11:41:33.000Z","msg":"講真加泰集會人多<br />\n但都幾失敗<br />\n因為冇平衡各方意見<br />\n變咗引起好大爭議<br />\n從而引起示威者分裂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔認同你加泰個例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0eb02e22f1f82f72b6711b25a2f127f31261f7d","tid":1676362,"uid":62151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T11:42:23.000Z","msg":"支持槍權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b7ca383beb1f31668d4f3ff3cc9d84bb741bd83","tid":1676362,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2cc0dd322f6c856966b918029df4afc340bad081","tid":1676362,"uid":86509,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T11:41:33.000Z","msg":"講真加泰集會人多<br />\n但都幾失敗<br />\n因為冇平衡各方意見<br />\n變咗引起好大爭議<br />\n從而引起示威者分裂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔認同你加泰個例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T11:42:39.000Z","msg":"因為加泰嗰個位本身就有爭議？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b97c3b56f9656b28041b4c38f2dc022ca5c9b29","tid":1676362,"uid":4783,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T11:43:36.000Z","msg":"心知唔講得出口真係on9到極致<br />\n唔講出口邊個知你支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講句野都自我審查，不如返屋企訓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b2486c908add827d13a5642340df1171ea2d02b","tid":1676362,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T11:52:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec6bea6487ab37d1e23ab808872edc0ac80d018c","tid":1676362,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T11:57:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4274fa4541518641bcb35bf04e5018da2ce257a","tid":1676362,"uid":82310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T11:59:07.000Z","msg":"主權方面，明明獨立就係erga omens right<br />\n決權方面，普選同自決就更加係中國攞走香港時答應既代價。<br />\n<br />\n怕講自己既合法合理權益，都算<br />\n人地講都要話人唔好講<br />\n說好的各有各做，說好的leaderless呢？"},{"pid":"5073e6f1101aa4d9a0bf3507b9d40cd5a68f621a","tid":1676362,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T12:18:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2daa32be69d98730a1641631600d3798946fd5a","tid":1676362,"uid":297997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T12:22:43.000Z","msg":"呢啲咪就係一直講個啲偽和理